params.description:
JSON-encoded string. Minimum shape with template:
  {"auth": {"key": "YOUR_AUTH_KEY"}, "template_id": "...", "fields": {...}}
Minimum shape inline:
  {"auth": {"key": "...", "expires": "2026-12-31T23:59:00.000Z"}, "steps": {"imported": {"robot": "/http/import", "url": "..."}, "encoded": {"use": "imported", "robot": "/video/encode", "preset": "ipad-high"}, "exported": {"use": "encoded", "robot": "/s3/store", "credentials": "my-aws"}}}
For signed Assemblies, also include "auth.expires" (ISO 8601, future). The `signature` form field then carries hex(HMAC-SHA384(params, secret)).
